The Cybersecurity Bootcamp at 4Geeks Academy is designed to equip individuals with no prior knowledge to become cybersecurity specialists. Over 16 weeks, students receive education in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with vital skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Classes are conducted live online, with a maximum of 16 participants, occurring three times a week. The program offers a recognized completion certificate, with no prior experience required for enrollment. Students can choose to learn in English or Spanish. For additional details, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. Stop.